negotiator.tournament

Class TournamentGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • negotiator.tournament.TournamentGenerator

  • public class TournamentGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will generate the party lists for each negotiation in a multi-party tournament. The reason for this generator is that the number of parties can become quite large, which means that at some point, we are unable to enumerate them all. This class will only give the next list parties to overcome that limitation.

    Agents in a tournament must be of class NegotiationParty.

    Author:
    Festen
